<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" WIDTH=40 HEIGHT=40 ALT=""></A>
Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="README"><B>README</B></a>
<DD>NOTE: This directory does NOT reflect the opinions or position of
    EFF, and is presented for informational purposes only, demonstrating
    online activism of one variety. EFF does not have a &quot;liberal&quot; or
    &quot;conservative&quot; stance, and is non-partisan
<DT><a href="labor_bbs.list"><B>labor_bbs.list</B></a>
<DD>Steve White's August 1994 list of BBSs addressing the
    concerns of the labor movement.
<DT><a href="labor_organizing_online.article"><B>labor_organizing_online.article</B></a>
<DD>August 1994 issue of Labor Week's
    article by Montieth Illingworth discussing the desire of many unions 
    to go online with particular focus on SoliNet.
<DT><a href="labor_resource.faq"><B>labor_resource.faq</B></a>
<DD>Rich Rose's April 1994 guide to internet resources
    pertaining to labor
</DL>

