other Internet censorship legislation
<DT><B><A HREF="/pub/Privacy/Email_GII_NII/">Email_GII_NII</a></B>
<DD>link to directory of info on GII/NII and other email/electronic
communications privacy and security issues.
<DT><B>EFF <A HREF="/pub/Net_info">Networking Information &amp; Tools</A>
Archive</B>
<DT><B>EFF's <A HREF=http://www.eff.org/papers/eegtti/"> Guide
to the Internet</A></B>


</DL>

