Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="README.Dist"><B>README.Dist</B></a>
<DD>how to get access to PGP and other cryptography software 
    distributions.
</DL>

<br><hr><br>
<H2><A NAME="dirs">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/filefolder_icon.gif"
ALT=""></A> Subdirectories in This Archive</H2>

<DL>
<DT><A HREF=".."><B>Up to the Parent Directory</B><P></a>
<DT><a href="Other/"><B>Other/</B></A>
<DD>directory reserved for other encryption programs (no contents 
    currently)
<DT><a href="RSA/"><B>RSA/</B></A>
<DD>directory containing RSA and RSAREF crypto tools such as PGP;
    US/Canadian access ONLY, due to export restrictions. These tools are
    in a hidden directory under RSA. To get to them, see the README.Dist
    file in the previous directory.
</DL>

