</PRE><HR>
<PRE>
This is the file "/privacy/README" on site "ftp.vortex.com",
located at Vortex Technology in Woodland Hills, California, U.S.A.

This directory ("/privacy") contains materials for the PRIVACY Forum,
including all issues of the PRIVACY Forum Digest and related materials;
they are indexed in the file "INDEX".

Files that end with ".Z" are in "compressed" format.  Be sure to do your
transfers in "binary" or "image" mode when retrieving these files.  If you
do not have an "uncompress" program, you may specify these files without the
".Z" and they will be automatically uncompressed for you during the transfer
process.  If you are going to use this automatic uncompression system
(i.e. leaving off the ".Z"), you should perform the transfer in
ordinary "ascii" mode, not in "binary" or "image" mode.

Any questions regarding these files should be directed to 
the address "privacy@vortex.com".
</PRE>
