<DD>Directory of information relating to various court cases
<DT><a href="CyberLaw_Course/"><B>CyberLaw_Course/</B></A>
<DD>Directory of lessons from the first online 'Cyberspace 
    Law for Non-Lawyers' Course (Alan Lewine, principal instructor).
<DT><a href="FOIA/"><B>FOIA/</B></A>
<DD>Directory of information relating to the Freedom of Information Act
    and similar open-government laws around the world.
