<DD>Directory of information of legal issues from other
    places
<DT><a href="Intellectual_property/"><B>Intellectual_property/</B></A>
<DD>Directory of information relating to intellectual
    property
<DT><a href="Internet_address_disputes/"><B>Internet_address_disputes/</B></A>
<DD>Link to directory of info on Internet
    address &amp; domain name disputes, proposals, conflicts, and problems,
    including legal cases, bills, and draft standards.
<DT><a href="Jurisdiction_and_sovereignty/"><B>Jurisdiction_and_sovereignty/</B></A>
<DD>Directory of info about jurisdiction and 
    sovereignty issues in cyberspace.
<DT><a href="Legal_Bytes_newsletter/"><B>Legal_Bytes_newsletter/</B></A>
<DD>Directory of back issues of the Legal Bytes
    Newsletter
<DT><a href="Legislation/"><B>Legislation/</B></A>
<DD>Directory of information relating to legislation
<DT><a href="Newin/"><B>Newin/</B></A>
<DD>Directory of miscellaneous information
<DT><a href="Raids_Digest/"><B>Raids_Digest/</B></A>
<DD>Directory containing back issues of Raids Digest - 
    e-newsletter of discussions and info regarding computer-related raids, 
    legal cases involving system operators, etc. Published by EFF-Austin.
<DT><a href="Tools/"><B>Tools/</B></A>
<DD>Directory of miscellaneous legal tools
</DL>

