This document was initially created by <A HREF="http://www.germany.eu.net/people/joke.html">J&ouml;rg Heitk&ouml;tter</A> on August 27, 1993.

The <EM>Texinfo</EM> edition originated from plain ASCII text file
<TT>`/pub/Net_info/Big_Dummy/bigdummy.txt'</TT> versions 1.0 to 2.2,
that was later renamed to <TT>`/pub/Net_info/EFF_Net_Guide/netguide.eff'</TT> version 2.21,
on the Electronic Frontier Foundation's server <B>ftp.eff.org</B>.
