<A HREF="http://www.iuc.org/www/molsen/"><STRONG>Internet Users
Consortium</STRONG></A>,<BR>
a fiercely independent Grass Roots organization founded by Martin Thompson
and Kenneth Koldys, Jr, to inform and coordinate Internet Users concerning
political and government actions against the complete self-actualization of the Internet and our Constitutional Rights in Cyberspace.</P> 
