<DL>
<DT><A href="art_21_constitution.japan"><B>art_21_constitution.japan</B></A>
    <DD>Article 21 of the Japanese Constitution, providing for freedom of 
    association, assembly, speech, press, and expression, freedom from 
    censorship, and a right to privacy.
</DL>

<br><hr><br>

<H2><A NAME="dirs">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/filefolder_icon.gif"
