text version is <A HREF="ftp://ftp.eff.org/pub/CAF/statements/cfp94.kadie">
ftp://ftp.eff.org/pub/CAF/statements/cfp94.kadie</a>.<p>
<p>

Via gopher as
<pre>
  gopher -p1/CAF gopher.eff.org
</pre>
then select "Academic Freedom Statements" and "Application of
Library Policy to Computers". Also see "Library Policy Statements"<p>

Via anonymous ftp to ftp.eff.org, directory /pub/CAF/statements, file
cfp94.kadie. Other files of possible interest are /pub/CAF/README and
/pub/CAF/caf and /pub/CAF/library/README.<p>

For email access, send email to ftpmail@decwrl.dec.com. Include the
