    Richey rejected the legitimacy of the FBI's claim that they needed to 
    delay the release of wiretap information. The article also contains 
    basic information about the case.
<DT><a href="epic_clipper_secrets.announce"><B>epic_clipper_secrets.announce</B></a>
<DD>EPIC press release regarding recently
    obtained FBI documents proving that the Clinton administration has been
    lying about its intentions to not make Clipper or other "key escrow" 
    schemes mandatory or to outlaw non-"escrowed" encryption. Aug. 1995.
</DL>

