Censorship in America</em><br>
Sara Diamond, <em>Spiritual Warfare: The Politics of the
Christian Right</em><br>
William A. Rusher, <em>The Rise of the Right</em><br>
Richard A. Viguerie, <em>The New Right: We're Ready to
Lead</em><br>
...and material provided by the listed organizations.<p>

<em>Written and compiled by James D'Entremont. Revised
version issued March 1, 1996.  As this document continues to
evolve, we welcome your questions, comments, and
corrections.
For more information send email to <A
HREF="mailto:kip@world.std.com">kip@world.std.com</A></em>


</DOC>
