<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/oz_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Information Infrastructure - Australia&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>ftp.eff.org/pub/GII_NII/Foreign_and_local/Australia/
<br>gopher.eff.org, 1/GII_NII/Foreign_and_local/Australia
<br>http://www.eff.org/pub/GII_NII/Foreign_and_local/Australia/
</H5>



