<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>EFF &quot;Legislation &amp; Regulation - Freedom Shrine: Historical Freedom Documents&quot; Archive</TITLE><LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:webmaster@eff.org"></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF" TEXT="000000" LINK="0000EE" VLINK="03066A" ALINK="FF0000">

