<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>K</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>
<H2><CENTER>K</CENTER></H2>
We lay on the shore<BR>
too busy thinking too much<BR>
to notice the starlight<BR>
fading away<BR>
fade into day<BR>
<P>
turning to her <BR>
resting restlessly on her elbows<BR>
legs bent at the knees<BR>
will you please love me forever<BR>
and never<BR>
<P>
shh she said<BR>
and buried my head<BR>
into her arms<BR>
and the dying alarms<BR>
floated away<BR>
away into day<BR>
</BODY></HTML>
</DOC>
