<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>EFF "Legal Cases - Privacy/FOIA - Gilmore v. NSA (Crypto Docs)" Archive</TITLE><LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:webmaster@eff.org"></HEAD><BODY>

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
