<BR><h2><A NAME="files"></a>
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" ALT=""></A>
Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="netgd_jp.sjis.gz"><B>netgd_jp.sjis.gz</B></a>
<DD>EFF Net Guide, Japanese (Kanji) version (SJIS-encoded 
    ASCII text, gzip-compressed). Currently at vers. 3.0.
<DT><a href="ngjpmsw6.zip"><B>ngjpmsw6.zip</B></a>
<DD>EFF Net Guide, Japanese (Kanji) version in a ZIP-compressed
    archive, consisting of Microsoft Word [presumably for Windows] 6.0 
    documents. Currently at vers. 3.0. This version is split into several
    files, by chapter. Not sure why; it just is.
<DT><a href="ngjpsjis.zip"><B>ngjpsjis.zip</B></a>
<DD>EFF Net Guide, Japanese (Kanji) version in a ZIP-compressed 
    archive, consisting of SJIS-encoded text files for DOS users. Currently
    at vers. 3.0. This version is split into several files, by chapter 
    since DOS/Win text viewers often cannot view large files.
</DL>

