<DT><a href="isdn_kapor_061391_ma_puc.testimony"><B>isdn_kapor_061391_ma_puc.testimony</B></a>
<DD>EFF Co-founder Mitchell Kapor's 
    testimony before the Massachusetts Department of Public Utilities.
    Kapor compares the computer industry of the late 70s and early 80s to 
    electronic communications today and urges the Dept. of Public Utilities 
    to ensure the availability of ISDN services at an affordable price.
