<TD><A HREF="http://www.eff.org/">EFFWeb Welcome Page</A></TD><h6></h6>
<TD><A HREF="http://www.eff.org/pub/Alerts/">Alerts</A></TD><h6></h6>
<TD><A HREF="http://www.eff.org/links.html#INDEXTOP">Topic Index</A></TD><h6></h6>
